如果您有其他具体问题或需要进一步的帮助，请告诉我！', 'text', NULL, NULL, '{"mode": "direct_rag_stream", "model_mode": "high", "first_token_ms": 737.1766999713145, "total_ms": 8408.83989998838}', '2026-06-16 05:02:07') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `conversation_id` = VALUES(`conversation_id`), `sequence_no` = VALUES(`sequence_no`), `role` = VALUES(`role`), `content` = VALUES(`content`), `content_type` = VALUES(`content_type`), `model_name` = VALUES(`model_name`), `token_count` = VALUES(`token_count`), `metadata_json` = VALUES(`metadata_json`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`);
