2、CHAR 列长度固定为创建表时声明的长度，长度值范围是 1 到 255 当 CHAR值被存储时，它们被用空格填充到特定长度，检索 CHAR 值
时需删除尾随空格。', '正确', 1, 20.0, 20.0, '{"correct_answer": "CHAR类型在存储时，其列长度是固定的，且当存储CHAR值时，会用空格填充到声明长度。", "hit_points": ["正确判断CHAR类型的存储特性：列长度固定且用空格填充"], "missing_points": [], "wrong_points": [], "comment": "您的判断完全正确。CHAR类型在存储时确实采用固定长度，并用空格填充到声明长度，这是其与VARCHAR类型的主要区别之一。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 08:37:54', '2026-06-18 08:41:18') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
INSERT INTO `exam_questions` (`exam_question_id`, `session_id`, `round_no`, `source_question_id`, `source_document_id`, `source_filename`, `source_page`, `section_path`, `question_type`, `prompt`, `options_json`, `correct_answer_json`, `reference_answer`, `user_answer`, `is_correct`, `score`, `max_score`, `analysis_json`, `status`, `created_at`, `answered_at`) VALUES ('exam_q_adcd266a44664b42a4f0f6bac0960137', 'exam_0bc691adb57c4da48a98d04ca58e0934', 4, 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2_outline_q_0841', 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2', 'Java面试题.pdf', 150, 'Spring Cloud面试题 / 27、springcloud断路器作用?', 'true_false', 'SpringCloud断路器的作用是通过完全打开、半开和关闭三种状态来防止因服务调用失败而导致的雪崩效应。', '["正确", "错误"]', '"正确"', '当一个服务调用另一个服务由于网络原因或自身原因出现问题，调用者就会等待被调用者的响应 当更多的服务请求到这些资源导致更多的
请求等待，发生连锁效应（雪崩效应）
断路器有完全打开状态:一段时间内 达到一定的次数无法调用 并且多次监测没有恢复的迹象 断路器完全打开 那么下次请求就不会请求到该
服务
半开:短时间内 有恢复迹象 断路器会将部分请求发给该服务，正常调用时 断路器关闭
关闭：当服务一直处于正常状态 能正常调用', '错误', 0, 0.0, 20.0, '{"correct_answer": "正确。SpringCloud断路器通过完全打开、半开和关闭三种状态来防止因服务调用失败而导致的雪崩效应。", "hit_points": [], "missing_points": ["正确识别断路器三种状态的作用"], "wrong_points": ["用户判定为错误，与标准答案不符"], "comment": "本题为判断题，标准答案为“正确”。用户给出的“错误”显然与正确理解相悖。断路器正是通过完全打开、半开和关闭三种状态来有效防止服务调用失败引发的雪崩效应，这是微服务架构中的核心保护机制。用户未能准确把握这一知识点，导致判断失误。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 08:37:59', '2026-06-18 08:41:50') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
