方法二：在日志中搜索密码并传递至请求标头中', '不会', 0, 0.0, 10.0, '{"correct_answer": "在src/main/resources目录下创建static文件夹，将JS文件放入其中（如static/js/myapp.js），然后在JSP页面中使用绝对路径引用：<script src=\\"/js/myapp.js\\"></script>。", "hit_points": [], "missing_points": ["说明将JS文件放入static文件夹", "通过绝对路径引用JS文件"], "wrong_points": [], "comment": "用户未作答，无法评分。本题要求简述在Spring Boot中添加并引用通用JS代码的步骤，正确答案涉及在resources/static下存放文件并使用绝对路径引用。建议学习相关知识点。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 09:32:35', '2026-06-18 09:35:01') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
INSERT INTO `exam_questions` (`exam_question_id`, `session_id`, `round_no`, `source_question_id`, `source_document_id`, `source_filename`, `source_page`, `section_path`, `question_type`, `prompt`, `options_json`, `correct_answer_json`, `reference_answer`, `user_answer`, `is_correct`, `score`, `max_score`, `analysis_json`, `status`, `created_at`, `answered_at`) VALUES ('exam_q_1687f88ef2e646868c360e5de89537b0', 'exam_537c6e09030848029fbf79429f389c76', 3, 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2_outline_q_0751', 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2', 'Java面试题.pdf', 130, 'Spring Boot面试题 / 25、如何使用 Spring Boot 实现分页和排序？', 'fill_blank', '在Spring Boot中，使用Spring Data JPA实现分页功能时，需要将____类型的参数传递给存储库方法。', '[]', '"Pageable"', '使用 Spring Boot 实现分页非常简单。使用 Spring Data-JPA 可以实现将可分页的传递给存储库方法。', 'Page', 0, 0.0, 10.0, '{"correct_answer": "Pageable", "hit_points": [], "missing_points": ["Pageable"], "wrong_points": ["Page"], "comment": "您填写的''Page''是返回的分页结果对象，但题目要求的是传递给存储库方法的参数类型，正确应为''Pageable''，请区分两者的作用。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 09:32:46', '2026-06-18 09:35:45') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
INSERT INTO `exam_questions` (`exam_question_id`, `session_id`, `round_no`, `source_question_id`, `source_document_id`, `source_filename`, `source_page`, `section_path`, `question_type`, `prompt`, `options_json`, `correct_answer_json`, `reference_answer`, `user_answer`, `is_correct`, `score`, `max_score`, `analysis_json`, `status`, `created_at`, `answered_at`) VALUES ('exam_q_63006b84316147febb5a31d691187057', 'exam_537c6e09030848029fbf79429f389c76', 4, 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2_outline_q_0776', 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2', 'Java面试题.pdf', 133, 'Spring Boot面试题 / 51、Spring Boot、Spring MVC 和 Spring 有什么区别？', 'single_choice', '关于Spring、Spring MVC和Spring Boot三者的描述，下列哪一项是正确的？', '["A", "A. Spring Framework的核心特征是依赖注入，所有Spring模块都基于依赖注入或控制反转。", "B. Spring MVC通过自动配置和启动项来解决Spring配置参数过多的问题。", "C. Spring Boot提供了一种分离式的方法来开发Web应用，使用DispatcherServlet等概念。"]', '"A"', 'SpringFrame
SpringFramework 最重要的特征是依赖注入。所有 SpringModules 不是依赖注入就是 IOC 控制反转。
当我们恰当的使用 DI 或者是 IOC 的时候，我们可以开发松耦合应用。松耦合应用的单元测试可以很容易的进行。
SpringMVC
Spring MVC 提供了一种分离式的方法来开发 Web 应用。通过运用像 DispatcherServelet，MoudlAndView 和 ViewResolver 等一些简单的
概念，开发 Web 应用将会变的非常简单。
SpringBoot
Spring 和 SpringMVC 的问题在于需要配置大量的参数。
Spring Boot 通过一个自动配置和启动的项来目解决这个问题。为了更快的构建产品就绪应用程序，Spring Boot 提供了一些非功能性特
征。', 'B. Spring MVC通过自动配置和启动项来解决Spring配置参数过多的问题。', 0, 0.0, 10.0, '{"correct_answer": "A. Spring Boot通过自动配置和启动项来解决Spring配置参数过多的问题", "hit_points": [], "missing_points": [], "wrong_points": ["将Spring Boot的自动配置和启动项特性错误地归因于Spring MVC"], "comment": "本题为单选题，标准答案为A。你的答案B错误地将Spring Boot的核心特性（自动配置和启动项）归因于Spring MVC，而实际上这些特性是Spring Boot专门用于简化Spring配置的。请仔细区分三个框架的不同职责。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 09:32:55', '2026-06-18 09:36:29') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
INSERT INTO `exam_questions` (`exam_question_id`, `session_id`, `round_no`, `source_question_id`, `source_document_id`, `source_filename`, `source_page`, `section_path`, `question_type`, `prompt`, `options_json`, `correct_answer_json`, `reference_answer`, `user_answer`, `is_correct`, `score`, `max_score`, `analysis_json`, `status`, `created_at`, `answered_at`) VALUES ('exam_q_92bba9829d6f441299675b90abf94c40', 'exam_537c6e09030848029fbf79429f389c76', 5, 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2_outline_q_0743', 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2', 'Java面试题.pdf', 129, 'Spring Boot面试题 / 16、如何集成 Spring Boot 和 ActiveMQ', 'true_false', '集成Spring Boot与ActiveMQ时，仅需引入spring-boot-starter-activemq依赖，配置量少且无需编写样板代码。', '["正确", "错误"]', '"正确"', '对于集成 Spring Boot 和 ActiveMQ，我们使用spring-boot-starter-activemq依赖关系。 它只需要很少的配置，并且不需要样板代码  
 
17、什么是 JavaConﬁg？  
Spring JavaConﬁg 是 Spring 社区的产品，它提供了配置 Spring IoC 容器的纯Java 方法。因此它有助于避免使用 XML 配置。使用 
JavaConﬁg 的优点在于：
1、面向对象的配置。由于配置被定义为 JavaConﬁg 中的类，因此用户可以充分利用 Java 中的面向对象功能。一个配置类可以继承另一
个，重写它的@Bean 方法等。
2、减少或消除 XML 配置。基于依赖注入原则的外化配置的好处已被证明。但是，许多开发人员不希望在 XML 和 Java 之间来回切换。
JavaConﬁg 为开发人员提供了一种纯 Java 方法来配置与 XML 配置概念相似的 Spring 容器。从技术角度来讲，只使用 JavaConﬁg 配置类来
配置容器是可行的，但实际上很多人认为将JavaConﬁg 与 XML 混合匹配是理想的。
3、类型安全和重构友好。JavaConﬁg 提供了一种类型安全的方法来配置 Spring容器。由于 Java 5.0 对泛型的支持，现在可以按类型而不是
按名称检索 bean，不需要任何强制转换或基于字符串的查找。', '错误', 0, 0.0, 10.0, '{"correct_answer": "集成Spring Boot与ActiveMQ时，只需引入spring-boot-starter-activemq依赖，配置量少且无需编写样板代码。", "hit_points": [], "missing_points": [], "wrong_points": ["用户判断为错误，但该表述符合Spring Boot Starter的自动配置特性，应为正确。"], "comment": "你的判断有误。Spring Boot通过starter自动配置机制能够大幅简化ActiveMQ的集成，引入spring-boot-starter-activemq后只需少量配置（甚至默认配置）即可使用，无需手动编写大量样板代码，故标准答案为正确。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 09:33:05', '2026-06-18 09:37:08') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
INSERT INTO `exam_questions` (`exam_question_id`, `session_id`, `round_no`, `source_question_id`, `source_document_id`, `source_filename`, `source_page`, `section_path`, `question_type`, `prompt`, `options_json`, `correct_answer_json`, `reference_answer`, `user_answer`, `is_correct`, `score`, `max_score`, `analysis_json`, `status`, `created_at`, `answered_at`) VALUES ('exam_q_08985b6a1cd74a5ca611fd9cc53fd541', 'exam_537c6e09030848029fbf79429f389c76', 6, 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2_outline_q_0766', 'doc_51ca3d8c1ca84e8b84f62b56d8c2abf2', 'Java面试题.pdf', 132, 'Spring Boot面试题 / 41、Spring Boot 自动配置原理是什么？', 'short_answer', '请简述Spring Boot自动配置的核心原理。', '[]', '"Spring Boot自动配置的核心依赖于@EnableAutoConfiguration、@Configuration和@ConditionalOnClass等注解。其中，自动配置类本质上是一个带有@Configuration注解的配置类，通过@ConditionalOnClass等条件注解根据类路径下是否存在指定的类来决定是否启用该自动配置。"', '注解 @EnableAutoConﬁguration, @Conﬁguration, @ConditionalOnClass 就是自动配置的核心，首先它得是一个配置文件，其次根据类
路径下是否有这个类去自动配置。', '1', 0, 0.0, 10.0, '{"correct_answer": "Spring Boot自动配置的核心原理依赖@EnableAutoConfiguration、@Configuration和@ConditionalOnClass等注解。自动配置类本质上是一个带有@Configuration的配置类，通过@ConditionalOnClass等条件注解判断类路径下是否存在指定类，从而决定是否启用自动配置。", "hit_points": [], "missing_points": ["未提及@EnableAutoConfiguration等关键注解", "未解释自动配置类与条件注解的关系", "未说明根据类路径条件启用配置的机制"], "wrong_points": ["答案仅为数字“1”，无有效内容"], "comment": "您的答案过于简略，未能体现任何自动配置的核心原理，建议仔细复习相关注解及条件加载机制。"}', 'answered', '2026-06-18 09:33:13', '2026-06-18 09:37:24') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `session_id` = VALUES(`session_id`), `round_no` = VALUES(`round_no`), `source_question_id` = VALUES(`source_question_id`), `source_document_id` = VALUES(`source_document_id`), `source_filename` = VALUES(`source_filename`), `source_page` = VALUES(`source_page`), `section_path` = VALUES(`section_path`), `question_type` = VALUES(`question_type`), `prompt` = VALUES(`prompt`), `options_json` = VALUES(`options_json`), `correct_answer_json` = VALUES(`correct_answer_json`), `reference_answer` = VALUES(`reference_answer`), `user_answer` = VALUES(`user_answer`), `is_correct` = VALUES(`is_correct`), `score` = VALUES(`score`), `max_score` = VALUES(`max_score`), `analysis_json` = VALUES(`analysis_json`), `status` = VALUES(`status`), `created_at` = VALUES(`created_at`), `answered_at` = VALUES(`answered_at`);
